      <title>逃亡国外的俄罗斯人回国推动普京的战时经济</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/russians-who-fled-war-return-in-boost-for-putin-s-war-economy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在克里姆林宫入侵乌克兰的第一年，就有多达一百万俄罗斯人逃亡国外。现在，数千人正在回国，为总统弗拉基米尔·普京带来了宣传上的胜利，并促进了他的战时经济。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/russians-who-fled-war-return-in-boost-for-putin-s-war-economy</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
