      <title>沙特阿拉伯加大对在线攻击以色列者的逮捕力度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/saudi-arabia-steps-up-gaza-arrests-as-israel-ties-edge-closer</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沙特阿拉伯加大了对在社交媒体上发布与以色列-哈马斯战争相关帖子的公民的逮捕力度，因为该国发出信号，准备同意与这个犹太国家建立外交关系。如果它致力于巴勒斯坦建国。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/saudi-arabia-steps-up-gaza-arrests-as-israel-ties-edge-closer</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 22:24:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国和沙特签署近邻防御协议旨在重塑中东</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/us-and-saudis-near-defense-pact-aimed-at-reshaping-middle-east</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，美国和沙特阿拉伯即将达成一项历史性协议，如果以色列政府结束加沙战争，该协议将为沙特提供安全保障，并为与以色列建立外交关系奠定可能的途径。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/us-and-saudis-near-defense-pact-aimed-at-reshaping-middle-east</guid>
